#

Baked Beef Lasagna with Bechamel Sauce and Spinach

$25
600 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

ItalianComfort FoodHeartyFamily Meal

Description

A decadent layered lasagna featuring rich beef, creamy bechamel, and fresh spinach for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • Lasagna noodles: 12 sheets
  • Ground beef: 1 lb
  • Onion: 1, diced
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Fresh spinach: 4 cups
  • Ricotta cheese: 15 oz
  • Mozzarella cheese: 2 cups, shredded
  • Parmesan cheese: 1 cup, grated
  • Egg: 1
  • Milk: 2 cups
  • Butter: 4 tbsp
  • Flour: 1/4 cup
  • Nutmeg: 1/4 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
